00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:05.000 
Ampleforth Organics are passionate about their products and customers.

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:13.000 
Martina and her team are responsible for connecting with customers and providing product demonstrations.

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:17.100 
Martina decides to rollout mobile devices to make connecting easier.  

00:00:18.100 --> 00:00:22.800 
When the team meet, they discuss how their mobile devices have changed the way they work.

00:00:22.900 --> 00:00:26.090 
It becomes clear that everyone in the team has had some mishaps.

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:32.800 
Kwame shares how he sent an unfinished email to a client accidentally. 

00:00:33.050 --> 00:00:40.000 
Jo shares they sent an embarrassing emoji to one of their longest standing suppliers. 

00:00:40.210 --> 00:00:49.900 
Martina explains a recent example where another person in the organisation forwarded an email containing sensitive information to one of their competitors.

00:00:50.250 --> 00:00:59.290 
The implications for careless communication can be very serious, leading to disciplinary action, legal issues, or financial penalties.

00:01:00.270 --> 00:01:07.120 
