00:01:24.120 --> 00:01:32.800 
The mobile devices enabled Martina and her team to sign up more customers than ever, and Jo patched up their relationship with their favourite customer.

00:01:33.200 --> 00:01:45.230 
By following a few key guidelines, Martina and her team can ensure they're taking the biggest steps towards being mindful of others, protecting themselves and their organisation.